{"tid":765455,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【飛機餐】國泰長途商務艙推香港風味 食牛腩河配楊枝甘露","createTime":"2018-08-02T18:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T17:21:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"835849982a10d0f41c5262f9552ea05c1a81423f","tid":765455,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T18:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180802/large/1533202660_7da5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180802%2Flarge%2F1533202660_7da5.jpg&h=1f5945c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國泰上月底調整商務艙餐單，前菜增至三款選擇，10小時以上航班有多達6道主菜選擇。值得一讚的是餐牌設計相當有心思，像一份飲食雜誌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飛美國或歐洲，回程時除了覺得疲倦，其實最想食一啖港式美食。國泰上月底更新長途航線商務艙的餐單，更推出「香港風味」系列，滿足一眾港人的胃口。系列包括蜜汁叉燒皇配薑葱撈麵、薑葱海鮮龍蝦湯泡飯、清湯牛腩河粉及楊枝甘露，將陸續推出更多菜式。為配合機艙烹調限制，選料亦有所調整，例如清湯牛腩河粉選用韓國燒烤所用的牛肋骨，避免肉質在高空加熱後變得粗糙。<br />\n<br />\n為令乘客感覺置身餐廳，商務艙餐單增加不少選擇，前菜增至3款包括湯，10小時以上航班更有6道主菜。如果不想吃得太heavy，乘客可選「輕盈膳食」作主菜，如口味清新的茴香小麥沙律，材料有慢煮番茄、巴馬臣芝士及香草醋汁。航程較長的北美洲及歐洲航班上，正餐間可選「最受乘客喜愛」餐點和小食，包括招牌漢堡及喇沙。<br />\n<br />\n此外，國泰推出一對一點餐服務，乘客可直接點前菜、主菜或甜品，毋須等其他人用餐完畢才逐道送上。乘客可於新推出的早餐卡上預選食物款式，如便捷早餐（丹麥酥餅配飲料）及傳統早餐（中式、西式及歐陸式），並自選送餐時間，不怕睡覺中途被叫醒。新餐單上月30日起逐步於長途航線商務艙推行，包括8月倫敦航線，9月法蘭克福、曼徹斯特及華盛頓航線等，計劃明年中完成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180802/large/1533202663_f044.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180802%2Flarge%2F1533202663_f044.jpg&h=5f330979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180802/large/1533202663_6078.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180802%2Flarge%2F1533202663_6078.jpg&h=49affdd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180802/large/1533202663_d8c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180802%2Flarge%2F1533202663_d8c1.jpg&h=4a5bd297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180802/large/1533202668_9b9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180802%2Flarge%2F1533202668_9b9d.jpg&h=4a34dddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180802/large/1533202667_1840.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180802%2Flarge%2F1533202667_1840.jpg&h=5992e546&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8678ad653798768b1e946c42a624f917e31bceae","tid":765455,"uid":5006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T19:22:28.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"b7872009ca2d69f35291bf1a89f1fc66f214edb5","tid":765455,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T19:28:08.000Z","msg":"竟然冇人踩因航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bd988557562d49a5a97b2782fa0a7ea3ab4065","tid":765455,"uid":61271,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T19:29:17.000Z","msg":"長途商務關我春事"},{"pid":"dd89b0d5d3ad1d8760eab839b53d96a5b21970f4","tid":765455,"uid":38648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T19:29:54.000Z","msg":"即係短途都係因卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af53692d828ad87d437f5f6808541baeef390e58","tid":765455,"uid":22243,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fb7e2c096d3191df7c061c8cda633e7dc041b5","tid":765455,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f5263c52673004558c44c19679ff9fe76f5dc8","tid":765455,"uid":11148,"